com.hp.ov.sdk.dto.storage

Class StorageSystem

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hp.ov.sdk.dto.BaseModelResource
      • com.hp.ov.sdk.dto.storage.StorageSystem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class StorageSystem
extends BaseModelResource
    The StorageSystem data transfer object (DTO) contains the information used to represent a storage system in the system. It is passed in to the add/update storage system REST api, as well as the add/update storage system through java client api.
